{"id":24592,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/24592","type":2,"name":"スクライド オルタレイション TAO","name_cn":"分身战士 ALTERATION TAO","summary":"今年是经典动画《分身战士》（s.CRY.ed）播出10周年，为纪念这一时刻，SUNRISE决定将重制这部动画，将原作全26话经数码润色，重新编排成上下两部，追加原创内容，而令人兴奋的是新作台词将重新录制。\r\n\r\n21世纪初的日本，原因不明的地壳变动使以横滨为中心，半径30公里的区域突然隆起，它从此以后被称为“Lost Ground”。由于日本政府在此地实行的街道复兴计划，使这个地方成为特殊的二层社会，这里的人被划分为住在复兴地区的“inner”和住在崩坏地区的“outer”，而不久之后在lost ground出生的人开始拥有一种叫“Alter”的超能力，他们以这种能力不断进行暴力和掠夺行为，人们都称他们为“Alter能力者”。为此，在“lost ground”的警察机关内成立了一支以同样拥有Alter能力的人为成员的部队“HOLY”，以应对事态。在这样的背景下，在崩坏地区成长的Alter能力者カズマ与HOLY所属的Alter能力者刘凤相遇了，故事也由此展开。","eps":[{"id":125827,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/125827","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"TAO","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-11-19","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2011-11-19","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":44,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":1,"6":14,"7":21,"8":7,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.7},"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/f4/d1/24592_c9c4X.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f4/d1/24592_c9c4X.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f4/d1/24592_c9c4X.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/f4/d1/24592_c9c4X.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/f4/d1/24592_c9c4X.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":58,"collect":57,"doing":1,"on_hold":6,"dropped":3},"crt":[{"id":8630,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/8630","name":"劉鳳","name_cn":"","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c3/38/8630_crt_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/c3/38/8630_crt_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/c3/38/8630_crt_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c3/38/8630_crt_anidb.jpg"},"comment":0,"collects":1,"info":{"gender":"男","alias":{"kana":"りゅう ほう","romaji":"Ryuu Hou","jp":"劉鳳"},"source":"anidb.net"},"actors":[{"id":3967,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/3967","name":"緑川光","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ad/f7/3967_prsn_MA707.jpg?r=1493708509","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/ad/f7/3967_prsn_